quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  22,65,"Enee, a tinaali wonndema Alla eltani on ko woni kon ka leydi, laa…óe …óen no dogira ka maaje Yamaruyee Makko on, hiMo jogitii kammu ngun fii wata ngu yanu e hoore leydi ndin si wonaa e duŇčayee Makko. Pellet, Alla ko O newanii…óo yim…ďe …ďen Yurmtee…óo […ďe]"
  22,66,Ko Kanko woni On wurnu…óo on refiti O wara on refti O wurnitoya on. Pellet ne…ó…óanke on ko o heewu…óo geddi
  22,67,"Men wa…óanii kala mofte laawol ngol …ďe rewata e mu'un, wata …ďe poo…óondir e maa…óa e fiyaake on, noddu faade ka Joomi maa…óa. Pellet, an hi…óa e hoore Laawol Focciingol"
  22,68,"Si …ďe wennjii ma, Maaku: \"Ko Alla woni Anndu…óo ko golloton kon"
  22,69,Alla √Ďaaway hakkunde mo'on √Ďalnde Darngal fii kon ko luutondirton fii mu'un
  22,70,"Enee, a anndaali wonndema Alla hiMo Anndi ko woni kon ka kammu e ka leydi, pellet, …óum no e nder Deftere. Pellet, …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] no newanii Alla"
  22,71,"Hi…ďe rewa gaanin Alla kon ko Dalil jippinaaka e fii mu'un, e kon ko ganndal alanaa …ďe e mu'un. Alanaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen walloowo"
  22,72,"Si jannganaama …ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen …ďanngu…óe a annday e geece …ďen yeddu…ďe mettinaare hi…ďe …óe…ďa yanude e …ďen jannganay…ďe …ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen. Maaku: \"Yo mi habru on ko …ďuri bonde e …óum moo…óon [ko jaŇčtana…óon kon] ko Yiite ngen Alla fodii nge …ďen yeddu…ďe bonii ruttorde"
